'''强热带风暴法茜'''（{{lang-en|Severe Tropical Storm Faxai}}，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]：WP202007，[[菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局|菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局]]：Juaning，-{zh-cn:台湾译名：'''法西'''; zh-hk:臺灣譯名：'''法西'''; zh-mo:臺灣譯名：'''法西'''; zh-tw:中國、香港、澳門譯名：'''法茜'''}-）是[[2007年太平洋台风季|2007年太平洋台风季]]的第20个获得命名的风暴，其持续时间较短，对陆地产生的影响也很小。法茜来源于10月下旬[[台风|西太平洋]]公海的一股热带低气压，系统在快速朝东北方向进发的过程中快速强化，于10月26日成为强热带风暴，不过到次日掠过[[日本|日本]]时，风暴已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，其残留于10月28日消散。

虽然法茜自始至终没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但与其相关联的[[雨带|外围雨带]]产生了暴雨，[[三宅岛|三宅岛]]的降雨量高达458[[毫米|毫米]]。一班飞往[[成田国际机场|成田国际机场]]的[[日本航空|日本航空]]航班在10月27日下午遭遇了严重的[[湍流|湍流]]，飞机因此受到损伤，机上有一人重伤，六人轻伤。[[东京|东京]]附近有一人在风暴经过时遇难，另外还有三人受伤。风暴造成的经济损失总计约为1.5亿[[日元|日元]]（合150万[[美元|美元]]）。

== 气象歷史 ==
{{storm path|Faxai 2007 track.png| alt=热带风暴路径图}}
热带风暴法茜源于10月24日位于[[关岛|关岛]]以西约805[[公里|公里]]一片持续存在的[[对流|对流]]带。卫星图像显示下层大气中有大范围环流转向，表面附近还存在[[低压槽|低压槽]]。对流围绕下层环流中心合并，其上层环境有利于系统发展，[[风切变|风切变]]较弱，外流发散程度也小<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-24 | accessdate = 2009-03-02 | title = Significant Tropical Weather Advisory for the Western and South Pacific Oceans | url = ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/GuamStuff/2007102415-ABPW.PGTW }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。次日，[[气象厅_(日本)|日本气象厅]]将此系统归类为热带低气压<ref name="JMABT">{{cite web |publisher=Japan Meteorological Agency | year = 2008 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = JMA Annual Tropical Cyclone Report for 2007 | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212234000/http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/AnnualReport/2007/Text/Text2007.pdf | url = http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/AnnualReport/2007/Text/Text2007.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]]}}</ref>。之后不久，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]因部分[[低气压|外层]]对流深化而发布[[热带气旋形成警报|热带气旋形成警报]]。由于北面有[[亚热带气旋|亚热带]][[高压脊|高压脊]]的影响，风暴朝西北方向行进<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-25 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = TCWC Advisories for October 25, 2007 at 12Z | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102512 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041245/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102512 }}</ref>。到了[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月26日0点，[[菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局|菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局]]把系统指定为热带低气压，并给其起了一个当地名称“{{lang|en|Juaning}}”<ref name="PAGASA">{{cite web | author = Philippine Atmospheric, Geophysical and Astronomical Services Administration | publisher = Typhoon 2000 | date = 2008-06-13 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = PAGASA Tropical Cyclone Warning Log | archivedate = 2012-02-13 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.maybagyo.com/stormarchives/2007/stormlogs/10juaning07_log.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213153008/http://www.maybagyo.com/stormarchives/2007/stormlogs/10juaning07_log.htm}}</ref>。日本气象厅大概也在同一时间将低气压升级为热带风暴并将其命名为“法茜”（{{lang|en|Faxai}}）<ref name="JMABT" />。

联合台风警报中心把法茜归类为第{{lang|en|20W}}号热带低气压<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-26 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = TCWC Advisories for October 26, 2007 at 00Z | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102600 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041307/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102600 }}</ref>。几个小时后，风暴开始向[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]过渡，风暴内的对流主要保持在其西北部分，而西南部分则有温度较低且干燥的空气进入<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-26 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = TCWC Advisories for October 26, 2007 at 06Z | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102606 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041318/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102606 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 }}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}中午12点，菲律宾大气地球物理和天文管理局发布了对“{{lang|en|Juaning}}”的最后一份公告，因为风暴已经离开其监控责任范围<ref name="PAGASA" />。联合台风警报中心报告第{{lang|en|20W}}号热带低气压已融入一片[[锋_(气象)|斜压区]]而转变成温带气旋。法茜的南部边缘发展出一片[[锋_(气象)|冷锋]]，这正是温带气旋的特点之一<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-26 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = TCWC Advisories for October 26, 2007 at 12Z | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102612 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041329/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102612 }}</ref>。不过就在这一时间左右，日本气象厅将法茜升级为强热带风暴，其10分钟的持续风速达到每小时95公里<ref name="JMABT" />。

随后不久，联合台风警报中心根据系统发展出一片明显的[[中心密集云團区|中心密集云團区]]而将低气压升级为热带风暴。[[朝鲜半岛|朝鲜半岛]]上空的一个短波[[低压槽|槽]]给法茜的增强提供了有利的上层环境<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | date = 2007-10-26 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = TCWC Advisories for October 26, 2007 at 18Z | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102618 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041340/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102618 }}</ref>。次日清晨，法茜开始迅速加速朝东北方向的中[[纬度|纬度]][[西风带|西风带]]前进。热带风暴与一个位于日本上空的[[反气旋|反气旋]]之间形成了强劲的[[气压梯度|气压梯度]]，令法茜的风场大幅向东北方向扩散。到联合台风警报中心发布最后一份公告时<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-10-27 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title=TCWC Advisories for October 27, 2007 at 00Z |url=http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102700 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005041351/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/archive/07102700 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-10-05 }}</ref>，他们估计风暴已经达到最高强度，一分钟的持续风速为每小时75公里<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |year=2008 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title=JTWC Best Track for Tropical Storm 20W (Faxai) |url=http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2007/2007s-bwp/bwp202007.txt |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005010628/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2007/2007s-bwp/bwp202007.txt |archivedate=2013-10-05}}</ref>。日本气象厅也估计法茜这时达到了最高强度，10分钟持续风速为每小时100公里，最低气压为975[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡_(单位)|百帕]]，28.79[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。但是[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]的报告中则认为法茜这个时候已经达到飓风强度，风速为每小时130公里<ref name="NOAArpt">{{cite web |author=George P. Bancroft |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2008-04 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title=Mariners Weather Log Volume 58 Number 1 |archivedate=2013-02-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130220184714/http://www.vos.noaa.gov/MWL/apr_08/northpacific.shtml |url=http://www.vos.noaa.gov/MWL/apr_08/northpacific.shtml}}</ref>。风暴接下来继续快速地向东北方向前进，并于{{lang|en|UTC}}10月27日中午12点左右在[[本州|本州]]东岸近海变成温带气旋。这股温带气旋残留之后保持了超过一天时间，于10月28日晚在开放海域上空消散<ref name="JMABT" />。不过美国国家海洋和大气管理局仍在继续对法茜的残留进行监控，该系统于10月29日到达[[阿留申群島|阿留申群島]]。次日，风暴快速强化，到{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点，其中心气压低至957毫巴（百帕）。10月31日，系统行进到[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]海域并减弱<ref name="NOAArpt" />。

日本气象厅在统计风速指标时使用的是10分钟的持续风速，而联合台风警报中心则使用的是1分钟持续风速<ref name="windchange">{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | year = 2005 | title = Frequently Asked Questions | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1 | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004062635/http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。两者间的换算系数为1.14<ref name="conversion">{{cite web | publisher = United States Navy | deadurl = yes | year = 2009 | url = http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/~chu/chap6/se200.htm | title = Section 2 Intensity Observation and Forecast Errors | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | archivedate = 2013-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510175941/http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/~chu/chap6/se200.htm }}</ref>。日本气象厅评估法茜在最高强度下的10分钟持续风速为每小时100公里，1分钟则为每小时120公里<ref name="JMABT" /><ref name="conversion" />。联合台风警报中心的数据则为10分钟持续风速每小时65公里，1分钟持续风速每小时75公里<ref name="conversion" /><ref name="JTWCBT">{{cite web | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005010628/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2007/2007s-bwp/bwp202007.txt | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2007/2007s-bwp/bwp202007.txt | year = 2008 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = JTWC Best Track for Tropical Storm 20W (Faxai)}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Faxai_26_oct_2007_0008Z.jpg|right]]
随着法茜接近日本，[[全日本空輸|全日本空輸]]取消了[[东京|东京]]到[[伊豆群島|伊豆群島]]之间的多個航班。东京到伊豆群岛及[[靜岡縣|靜岡縣]]的部分渡轮也因风暴而取消。东京周边区域获得通知，准备应对狂风、暴雨和高达6米的巨浪<ref name="BN1">{{cite web |author=Ron Rhodes |publisher=Bloomberg News |date=2007-10-27 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title= Typhoon Faxai Nears Central Japan; Flights Canceled (Update1) |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121024031345/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=ajfFElYhmfWU&refer=home |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=ajfFElYhmfWU&refer=home}}</ref>。居民收到警告，风暴来袭期间，特别是日落以后要留在室内，以免为飞溅的碎片所伤<ref>{{cite web | author = {{lang|ja|増田雅昭}} | publisher = Yahoo Japan Corporation | date = 2007-10-27 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | script-title = ja:韋駄天（いだてん）台風、接近中 | url = http://blogs.yahoo.co.jp/wth_map/50108417.html | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120222040151/http://blogs.yahoo.co.jp/wth_map/50108417.html}}</ref>。

虽然法茜自始至终没有实现登陆，但其外围[[雨带|雨带]]产生了暴雨，给日本东海岸部分地区造成了轻微的损失<ref name="tcr" />。降雨量最高的[[三宅岛|三宅岛]]达458毫米，而东京的[[大島支廳_(東京都)|大島支廳]]也有192毫米<ref name="Rainfall" />。三宅岛的降雨量已经接近其10月27日的最高降雨纪录<ref>{{cite web |author=Staff Writer |publisher=''Earthweek: A Diary of the Planet'' |date=2007-11-02 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title=Tropical Storm Faxai Drenches Parts of Japan |url=http://www.earthweek.com/online/ew071102/ew071102f.html |archivedate=2012-02-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214111745/http://www.earthweek.com/online/ew071102/ew071102f.html}}</ref>。还有部分地区降雨量达到95毫米<ref name="Rainfall">{{cite web |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |year=2007 |accessdate=2013-12-19 |title=Japan Rainfall for October 25 to 28, 2007 |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/summary_prec.pl?id=200720&lang=en&sort=total&order=dec&stype=number |archive-date=2019-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190304141209/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/summary_prec.pl?id=200720&lang=en&sort=total&order=dec&stype=number |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在全国范围内共计引发了七场[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref name="tcr" />。关东地方位于东京附近区域有一位女性丧生<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Earth Environment Service | date = 2007-11-02 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = Tropical Storm Faxai Drenches Parts of Japan |url=http://www.earthweek.com/online/ew071102/ew071102f.html | archivedate = 2012-02-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120214111745/http://www.earthweek.com/online/ew071102/ew071102f.html}}</ref>，还有三人受伤。风暴还造成一户民宅、两[[公顷|公顷]][[农田|农田]]、两公里道路以及一艘船受损。整个日本共有9605户居民家中因这场风暴而停电，经济损失共计为1.5亿日元（合150万美元）<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Japan Meteorological Agency | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2008 | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = 41st Session Country Report: Japan | url = http://www.typhooncommittee.org/41st/docs/item%206/Japan.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120220011020/http://www.typhooncommittee.org/41st/docs/item%206/Japan.pdf |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

[[日本标准时间|日本标准时间]]10月27日下午17点31分，一架前往[[成田国际机场|成田国际机场]]的[[日本航空|日本航空]][[波音767|波音767-300]]客机在距[[成田市|成田市]]东南方向约74公里时遭遇到来自法茜的强烈[[湍流|湍流]]，导致飞机出现损伤，机上一共有七人受伤，其中一人伤势严重<ref>{{cite web | author = Japan Airlines | publisher = Japan Transport Safety Board | date = 2008-12-19 | archivedate = 2013-04-01 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | title = Aircraft Accident Investigation Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130401121841/http://www.mlit.go.jp//jtsb/eng-air_report/JA611J.pdf | url = http://www.mlit.go.jp/jtsb/eng-air_report/JA611J.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。

